    "composer": "Noel Rosa / Ismael Silva 1934",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>   7      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se não mandei você embora, em fim foi porque me faltou a coragem</span>\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m7\">G#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas se você vai dá o fora, então passe bem,     boa viagem.</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O amor é como a chama, tem princípio, meio e fim, se você já não</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me ama para que fingir assim? Não mandei você embora porque sou</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m7\">G#m7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Benevolente,para que você agora quer sai ocultamente?</span>\n\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se não mandei você embora, em fim foi porque me faltou a coragem</span>\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m7\">G#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas se você vai dá o fora, então passe bem, boa viagem.</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Seu desejo não me assombra, ofereço meu auxílio</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Passe bem vá pela sombra, acabou-se o nosso edílio.</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m7\">G#m7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Seu amor e o seu nome eu também vou esquecer, desta vez juntou-se</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A fome com a vontade de comer.</span>\n\n(solo 2x) <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m7\">G#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span> \n",
